<p>
<note n="0754001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0754001">徙＝從【元】</note>
<note n="0754002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0754002">歛＝斂【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0754003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0754003">享＝亨【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0754004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0754004">枝＝支【宋】</note>
<note n="0754005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0754005">慘＝參【元】</note>
<note n="0756001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0756001">厖＝尨【宋】</note>
<note n="0756002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0756002">耶＝邪【宋】【元】</note>
